query: DELETE m FROM measurements m LEFT JOIN (SELECT MIN(id) as min_id, studentId, DATE(measureDate) as measureDate FROM measurements GROUP BY studentId, DATE(measureDate)) keep ON m.id = keep.min_id WHERE keep.min_id IS NULL;
